FREE Tie Dye Event in Victory Park

Join us anytime between 6-8pm for cool treats and color dyes to turn your plain white tees into masterpieces.

Options to buy shirts from us or bring your own.

Registration is required

RoFo Kids Nature Program

Welcome back to our lovely RoFo Kids Nature program for Ages 3-5 & 6-8. We offer 2 sessions 1 Saturday a month Spring - Fall.

This event will take place at the Trestle Bridge - meet us at the Pink Moose to check in.

Registration is required for this FREE event. Registration opens up 2 weeks prior to each event.

Earth Day Clean Up in Victory Park

Grab your friends, trash bags and good will to help us clean up Victory Park and the surrounding areas. We will provide the trash bags! We just need your helping hands on this special day for mother nature.
